<SYNC Start=11801><P Class=KRCC>
opened for all app developers to register and
<SYNC Start=14200><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=14201><P Class=KRCC>
start publishing their apps without any review or
<SYNC Start=17150><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=17151><P Class=KRCC>
validation requirements from Google, OEMs, or carriers. For
<SYNC Start=21910><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=21911><P Class=KRCC>
us as developers, the ability to distribute apps and
<SYNC Start=25065><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=25066><P Class=KRCC>
the possibility of monetizing them through up front payments
<SYNC Start=28300><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=28301><P Class=KRCC>
in app billing and advertising directly to the owners of
<SYNC Start=31320><P Class=KRCC>
