but as those first 50 apps quickly grew to
<SYNC Start=91910><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=91911><P Class=KRCC>
hundreds, thousands, and now over a million apps, it takes
<SYNC Start=95300><P Class=KRCC>
