<SYNC Start=95301><P Class=KRCC>
a lot more than speed to stand out in
<SYNC Start=97710><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=97711><P Class=KRCC>
the crowd. These days the tables stakes are a base
<SYNC Start=101320><P Class=KRCC>
