<SYNC Start=101321><P Class=KRCC>
line of quality and willingness to create great experiences
<SYNC Start=104830><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=104831><P Class=KRCC>
for all your users. Of course app quality can
<SYNC Start=108500><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=108501><P Class=KRCC>
be somewhat subjective, but over the years we've identified
<SYNC Start=112360><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=112361><P Class=KRCC>
the core criteria that users identify with apps of
<SYNC Start=115200><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=115201><P Class=KRCC>
high quality. And to make your life easier, they're
<SYNC Start=118130><P Class=KRCC>
