<SYNC Start=139410><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=139411><P Class=KRCC>
your app is stable and performant. So, with over
<SYNC Start=142860><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=142861><P Class=KRCC>
a million apps already available in Google Play it's
<SYNC Start=145780><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=145781><P Class=KRCC>
